# Copy to `.env` for local dev, or set these as GitHub repo *Variables* for prod.
# Everything here is a PUBLIC client identifier — never put secrets in this file.

# ── Deploy target (defaults match GitHub Pages; see astro.config.mjs) ──────────
# SITE_URL=https://michaeljgrimm.github.io
# BASE_PATH=/llmreference

# ── Analytics (off until a provider is set) ───────────────────────────────────
# Choose ONE provider and fill in its required field(s). See docs/SEO.md.
#
# plausible:   set PROVIDER + DOMAIN (+ optional SRC for self-hosted script)
# cloudflare:  set PROVIDER + TOKEN (Web Analytics beacon token)
# goatcounter: set PROVIDER + SRC   (your https://<you>.goatcounter.com/count endpoint)
# umami:       set PROVIDER + SRC (script URL) + TOKEN (website id)
#
# PUBLIC_ANALYTICS_PROVIDER=plausible
# PUBLIC_ANALYTICS_DOMAIN=llmreference.com
# PUBLIC_ANALYTICS_SRC=
# PUBLIC_ANALYTICS_TOKEN=
